This is the redistribution of two packages: hz2ps-2.0, and hzbdf.
Send bugs and comments to the author of these two packages.
See individual files for copyright and permission notices.
Use at your own risk and I disclaim all kinds of warranty.

Packages "hz2ps-2.0" contains a program "hz2ps".
Packages "hzbdf" contains programs "bdf2hzfont", "hzfont2bdf".

"hz2ps" can be used to print GB encoding and HKU Big5 encoding
Chinese text in a Postscript printer.

"hz2ps" needs HZ format fonts.  You can get them from somewhere else,
or, you can convert them from X11 BDF fonts (located in ../../fonts)
by program "bdf2hzfont".
